# Bank Statement Template

## SHEET 1 - SUMMARY/DASHBOARD

### BORROWER/LOAN INFORMATION
| Today’s Date | Completed By | Borrower Name | Employee Name | Account Number | Loan Number | Account Type |
|--------------|--------------|---------------|----------------|----------------|-------------|--------------|

### LARGE DEPOSIT FLAG
| Average Deposit | Percentage Amount | Large Deposit Threshold |
|-----------------|--------------------|--------------------------|

### TOTALS
| Total Deposits | =SUMIF(Transactions!E:E,"Include",Transactions!C:C) |
|----------------|------------------------|
| Total Included Deposits | =SUMIF(Transactions!E:E,"Include",Transactions!C:C) |
|----------------------------|------------------------|
| Total Excluded Deposits | =SUMIF(Transactions!E:E,"Exclude",Transactions!C:C) |
|-------------------------|-------------------|
| Total Debits | =SUMIF(Debits!D:D,"Include",Debits!C:C) |
|-------------------|------------------|
| Total Included Debits | =SUMIF(Debits!D:D,"Include",Debits!C:C) |
|----------------------------|----------------|
| Total Excluded Debits | =SUMIF(Debits!D:D,"Exclude",Debits!C:C) |
|----------------------------|-------------------|
| Qualifying Income Avg | =AVERAGEIF(Transactions!D:D,"PAYROLL",Transactions!C:C) |
|------------------------|--------------------------|

### BREAKDOWN BY TRANSACTION TYPE
| Transaction Type | Included Total | Excluded Total | Count |
|------------------|----------------|----------------|-------|
| ATM_DEPOSIT      | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"ATM_DEPOSIT",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"ATM_DEPOSIT",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"ATM_DEPOSIT",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| PAYROLL          | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"PAYROLL",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"PAYROLL",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"PAYROLL",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| ZELLE            | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"ZELLE",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"ZELLE",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"ZELLE",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| OTHER            | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"OTHER",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"OTHER",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"OTHER",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| TRANSFER         | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"TRANSFER",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"TRANSFER",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"TRANSFER",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| DIRECT_DEPOSIT    | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"DIRECT_DEPOSIT",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"DIRECT_DEPOSIT",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"DIRECT_DEPOSIT",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| REFUNDS           | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"REFUNDS",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"REFUNDS",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"REFUNDS",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| UNEMPLOYMENT     | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"UNEMPLOYMENT",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"UNEMPLOYMENT",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"UNEMPLOYMENT",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| LOAN_DEPOSITS    | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"LOAN_DEPOSITS",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"LOAN_DEPOSITS",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"LOAN_DEPOSITS",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |
| TAX_RETURN       | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"TAX_RETURN",Transactions!E:E,"Include") | =SUMIFS(Transactions!C:C,Transactions!D:D,"TAX_RETURN",Transactions!E:E,"Exclude") | =COUNTIFS(Transactions!D:D,"TAX_RETURN",Transactions!E:E,"Include") |

